      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted 996.2 Carrera 4S, featuring the 3.6L M96 horizontally-opposed six-cylinder engine with VarioCam Plus. This wide-body variant delivers power through a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle and a viscous-coupling AWD system. The IMS bearing and rear main seal (RMS) have been proactively addressed, ensuring the integrity of the rotating assembly. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers provide excellent thermal management and stopping power. While showing minor patina from regular use, the drivetrain and chassis are dialed for immediate performance.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Reliable daily driver. Title in hand.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and value. This car features a gleaming exterior with only minor, age-appropriate road wear, complemented by a smoke-free interior where the premium upholstery remains supple and clean. Mechanically, it stands in excellent health; I have strictly followed all manufacturer-recommended service intervals, and the engine runs as smoothly as the day it was driven off the lot. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring the next owner enjoys a turn-key experience. From the responsive handling to the crystal-clear premium sound system and power sunroof, every feature functions exactly as intended. It\u2019s a reliable, polished ride for someone who appreciates a car that has been treated with respect and care.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
