    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? This car has been such a joy to own and is still in wonderful shape for its next owner. It runs like a dream and has been well-cared for, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or spontaneous road trips. It\u2019s got a lot of heart and is ready to hit the road today\u2014come see why I've loved driving it so much!",
