    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six, an engine renowned for its high-revving nature and individual throttle bodies. This example utilizes the 6-speed Getrag manual transmission for direct gear engagement and features a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a precise valve clearance adjustment to maintain the integrity of the dual-VANOS system. The suspension maintains its composure through upgraded bushings, ensuring the chassis handles high-lateral loads with minimal deflection. While the exterior and interior present with an honest patina consistent with its 'good' status, the powertrain remains robust and responsive. This is an enthusiast-spec driver\u2019s car optimized for peak atmospheric performance.",
